{"tid":466913,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能揾到呢個手鐲？","createTime":"2017-11-13T04:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T07:25:33.000Z","uid":10873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff2173a6eb20e458b4c0e1f94cd71685738d397d","tid":466913,"uid":10873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/121037_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F121037_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c96e2047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟因一次打波整唔見左，雖然女友無嬲但我真係內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經試過上網揾但係都揾唔到，所以想大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全新/二手都得，唔該哂各位絲巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ccba97f846e3711706f9a68741797c08d04561","tid":466913,"uid":7430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:17:19.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n上網買過隻 仲要2手就無意義啦<br />\n應該親手整返一對囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有 你女朋友一定有嬲 佢只係扮唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e21b5fb72dae6865946115cccc3eef6595e2293","tid":466913,"uid":10873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n上網買過隻 仲要2手就無意義啦<br />\n應該親手整返一對囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有 你女朋友一定有嬲 佢只係扮唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺佢只係扮唔嬲，好啦唯有照你咁講整過對啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502ac230d2c574346a0fa68b431fab5f4557be05","tid":466913,"uid":71199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"買返對同牌子嘅一齊戴啦一係，再應承佢唔會再整唔見<br />\n<br />\n如果真係想搵返同款不如去專門店問下仲有冇出<br />\n呢隻牌子應該唔難搵"},{"pid":"e9deec0d3f3bc24fb4a4add395851c3e37229309","tid":466913,"uid":3077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"琴日係觀塘果間專門店好似見到有一隻類似嘅<br />\n不過唔係銀色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望你搵到喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831bde992e3f2680a02213a0d7c4a5b84ed792ba","tid":466913,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌<br />\n上網買過隻 仲要2手就無意義啦<br />\n應該親手整返一對囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有 你女朋友一定有嬲 佢只係扮唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺佢只係扮唔嬲，好啦唯有照你咁講整過對啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前親手整過一對比男朋友<br />\n佢好鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d5bccd8158f4462303b8f098589a21d2123e02","tid":466913,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:15:34.000Z","msg":"fb好多銀器店都係咁上下樣"},{"pid":"19dba6aba765bbc720b67e740c32c549369720a2","tid":466913,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a85527a071c70cb8a8cf7f0db72e0f4db97d9d65","tid":466913,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:25:33.000Z","msg":"差唔多啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/152524_82e7f5a175bc739abd2913b99cb6aa4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F152524_82e7f5a175bc739abd2913b99cb6aa4e.jpg&h=ba2e58d5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}